Package: ghostty
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast, feature-rich, cross-platform terminal emulator
 Ghostty is a terminal emulator that uses platform-native UI and GPU
 acceleration for enhanced performance and visual quality.
 .
 Features include GPU acceleration, ligature support, custom shaders,
 and native OS integration for macOS, Linux, and Windows.

Package: libghostty-vt-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ghostty (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Section: libdevel
Description: Development files for Ghostty VT library
 Development files for the Ghostty VT library, including headers,
 pkg-config metadata, and the development shared object symlinks.
